reviewText: If you have never been to a Woody car show this is the video to have, it covers the Ron Jon Surf show at the Block of Orange and the L.A. Wood show in San Pedro, the announcer walks around the show and highlights different cars for their rarity and uniqueness, during this time interviewing the owners and giving a complete detailed history of each vehicle. If you don't own one of these beauties, you will want to after watching this video.
